"{\"uid\": \"rvasia.org-asian-news-drag-queens-admit-paris-olympic-games-performance-parody-last-supper\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The artists involved in the opening ceremony of the 2024 Olympic Games have disclosed that their performance was, in fact,a parody of Leonardo da Vinci's \\\"The Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5802574483457463e-17, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The artists\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 11}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 24, \"to\": 44}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 70}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 108}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"a parody\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The admission was made in online social media posts and statements to the media.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The admission\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 187}, {\"ngram\": \"online social media posts\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 225}, {\"ngram\": \"statements\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to the French media, Piche, a drag queen and rapper, said the performance was a tableau of the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9997834172451977, \"rank\": 0.00021446814551114203, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Piche\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"a drag queen\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"rapper\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"a tableau\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The worldwide backlash showed that \\\"we have succeeded and we have done what had to be done, that we have been fair and representative,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The worldwide backlash\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Art always divides,\\\" Piche said.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Art\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"Piche\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As long as it does not move people, it's not art for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he insisted the parody of the Last Supper \\\"is not a provocation\\\" and justified it by saying \\\"it's a biblical representation that has been reused in pop culture for decades and it's never really been a problem.\\\"\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the parody\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"a provocation\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"a biblical representation\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"pop culture\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Piche denied any intention to provoke Christians and that there was nothing offensive in the show.\", \"from\": 83